♪This love is full of regrets♪

9
00:00:33,300 --> 00:00:37,420
♪You are but a dream
in this fleeting life♪

10
00:00:40,260 --> 00:00:41,260
[Part For Ever]

11
00:00:41,260 --> 00:00:42,000
[Adapted from the novel by Jing Mo,]

12
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:42,900
[My Lord,
Madam Doesn't Want to See You Again]

13
00:00:42,900 --> 00:00:44,780
[Episode 5]

14
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:02,240
As long as you spare them,

15
00:01:03,430 --> 00:01:05,310
I'm willing

16
00:01:06,680 --> 00:01:08,120
to accept any punishment.

17
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:18,230
I don't understand

18
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:21,040
why you're doing this.

19
00:01:22,590 --> 00:01:24,590
I'm willing to give up everything.

20
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:27,480
I only ask you to let them go.

21
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:33,400
You're overestimating yourself.

22
00:01:33,710 --> 00:01:34,310
You...

23
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:37,710
Taking their lives

24
00:01:38,230 --> 00:01:40,120
is as simple as crushing an ant.

25
00:01:40,760 --> 00:01:42,120
Tomorrow is the succession ceremony.

26
00:01:42,430 --> 00:01:43,590
You better behave

27
00:01:43,590 --> 00:01:44,920
and stop playing tricks.

28
00:01:48,070 --> 00:01:48,870
Ling Xiao,

29
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:50,870
I've arranged a good show

30
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:54,120
for your succession ceremony tomorrow.

31
00:01:55,070 --> 00:01:56,480
The case of my father's suicide

32
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:57,640
is still unclear.

33
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,640
I must return to the City Lord's Mansion

34
00:01:59,950 --> 00:02:00,870
to find out the truth.

35
00:02:01,430 --> 00:02:02,480
But you're alone.

36
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,870
Don't worry. I have a plan.

37
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:04,870
I just need

38
00:02:05,870 --> 00:02:07,430
your help.

39
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:29,520
You should know the consequences

40
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:32,190
of playing tricks.

41
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:39,310
The succession ceremony concerns
the reputation of Canglong City.

42
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:42,080
How could I do anything
to harm Canglong City

43
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:44,800
just to go against you?

44
00:02:54,630 --> 00:02:56,630
[Ling]
The auspicious time has arrived!

45
00:02:56,630 --> 00:02:59,360
May His Lordship and Her Ladyship

46
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:01,360
come forward to pay respects!

47
00:03:52,630 --> 00:03:54,400
Are you deliberately
attracting attention

48
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,680
and inviting criticism?

49
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:11,120
The ceremony begins now!

50
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:14,240
May we ask His Lordship and Her Ladyship

51
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:16,190
to pay respects to the former City Lord!

52
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:27,270
Where is Ling Xiao?

53
00:04:35,430 --> 00:04:37,120
Father, I'm Wan'er.

54
00:04:37,430 --> 00:04:39,240
Were you harmed by traitors?

55
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:41,630
Now all the people
of Canglong City are here.

56
00:04:41,750 --> 00:04:44,120
You can tell the truth to the world.

57
00:04:45,390 --> 00:04:47,360
I made a huge mistake

58
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:49,430
and can only end my life to atone.

59
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,310
It's the cycle of heaven's justice.

60
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:54,480
This is all my retribution.

61
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:57,120
That's impossible. You're...

62
00:04:57,310 --> 00:05:00,040
Ling Xiao, you are decisive

63
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,480
and diligent.

64
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:03,190
A rare talent.

65
00:05:03,750 --> 00:05:07,430
The position of Canglong City's
City Lord belongs to you.

66
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:10,360
Thank you for your appreciation.

67
00:05:10,630 --> 00:05:11,750
I, Ling Xiao,

68
00:05:11,750 --> 00:05:15,190
shall not disappoint you
and your kindness.

69
00:05:16,830 --> 00:05:17,920
It was you.

70
00:05:20,830 --> 00:05:22,270
I should thank you

71
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:25,120
for helping me secure
the position of City Lord.

72
00:05:36,870 --> 00:05:39,070
Blessings to His Lordship!

73
00:05:42,110 --> 00:05:44,520
Blessings to His Lordship!

74
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:49,390
May His Lordship and Her Ladyship

75
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:51,510
pay respects to heaven and earth.

76
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,270
Heavenly fire has descended!

77
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:15,120
- It's on fire!
- It's on fire!

78
00:06:19,860 --> 00:06:21,610
It's on fire!

79
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,040
I didn't expect you

80
00:06:25,630 --> 00:06:27,360
to prepare such a masterpiece for me.

81
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,830
I have nothing to do with this.

82
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:29,950
My Lord!

83
00:06:29,950 --> 00:06:30,600
Ling!

84
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:31,720
Miss Niyue, be careful.

85
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:32,820
- Ling!
- My Lord!

86
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:37,680
Run! It's on fire!

87
00:06:39,630 --> 00:06:40,950
The fire is getting bigger.

88
00:06:40,950 --> 00:06:42,070
We can't wait here to die.

89
00:06:44,870 --> 00:06:46,680
If we go against the wind,
it will keep us from getting burned.

90
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,270
The wind is currently blowing...

91
00:06:48,430 --> 00:06:50,600
The wind is currently blowing
from the east.

92
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,040
My father said,

93
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,600
as long as we go against the wind,

94
00:06:53,750 --> 00:06:55,240
we won't get burned.

95
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,160
There's a lot of vegetation here,

96
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,430
which burns easily.

97
00:06:58,870 --> 00:06:59,920
We must act quickly.

98
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:02,160
Let's use the fire to escape now.

99
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:04,720
All right. I'll be your eyes.

100
00:07:09,310 --> 00:07:10,120
Watch out!

101
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,360
Hurry! Put out the fire!

102
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:15,120
My Lord!

103
00:07:15,430 --> 00:07:16,190
Are you all right?

104
00:07:16,940 --> 00:07:23,700
♪I think of you again
as I write down the past memories♪

105
00:07:23,900 --> 00:07:29,740
♪Who did I share my emotions
during those years?♪

106
00:07:30,180 --> 00:07:36,980
♪Threads of emotions linger,
deeply immersed in your features♪

107
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:38,950
Watch out!

108
00:07:42,660 --> 00:07:50,100
♪The clear wind points to the love
and separation, so poignant♪

109
00:07:53,310 --> 00:07:55,510
If we go against the wind,
it will keep us from getting burned.

110
00:07:55,510 --> 00:07:58,630
As long as we go against the wind,
we won't get burned.

111
00:07:59,310 --> 00:08:02,360
Don't be scared. Let's go this way.

112
00:08:03,380 --> 00:08:05,980
♪To the ending♪

113
00:08:06,100 --> 00:08:10,140
♪With the flowers falling
and the time passing♪

114
00:08:10,260 --> 00:08:12,540
♪Leaving only memories behind♪

115
00:08:12,660 --> 00:08:16,580
♪The wind blows from a long distance♪

116
00:08:16,780 --> 00:08:19,620
♪Yet, you didn't show up♪

117
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:24,870
Thank you.

118
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:28,040
If you hadn't come up with the plan
to escape through the fire,

119
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,830
I wouldn't have been able to escape.

120
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:32,480
I should thank you for being my eyes.

121
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:34,870
To celebrate our escape,

122
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:38,360
I'll give you a rabbit-shaped pendant

123
00:08:38,670 --> 00:08:39,870
I carved myself.

124
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:45,550
I really want to see
what this rabbit looks like.

125
00:08:45,980 --> 00:08:52,500
♪This love is full of regrets.
You're a dream in this fleeting life♪

126
00:08:53,630 --> 00:08:55,790
Instead of fussing
over small matters like verbal thanks,

127
00:08:56,870 --> 00:08:58,150
it's better to take action

128
00:08:58,360 --> 00:09:00,240
to solve the arson case.

129
00:09:07,150 --> 00:09:09,320
Ling, I prepared medicine for you.

130
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:10,630
It's very effective for healing burns

131
00:09:10,630 --> 00:09:12,080
and removing scars.

132
00:09:12,150 --> 00:09:12,960
It's just a minor injury.

133
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,510
Even a minor injury
shouldn't be taken lightly.

134
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,840
I'd be heartbroken if it left a scar.

135
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:22,480
No matter.

136
00:09:34,630 --> 00:09:35,390
Ling,

137
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:38,240
I know you kept me by your side

138
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,600
out of gratitude
for saving you back then.

139
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:43,150
Now, you have your wife by your side.

140
00:09:43,870 --> 00:09:45,480
I've forgotten my place when it comes

141
00:09:47,910 --> 00:09:49,030
to applying medicine for your injuries.

142
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:09,790
Your eyes are healed.

143
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:18,840
Niyue,

144
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,320
don't overthink it.

145
00:10:22,030 --> 00:10:22,840
Give me the medicine.

146
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:03,030
What are you sneaking around here?

147
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:07,390
You were the one who came here
without making a sound.

148
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:08,360
Oh?

149
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,120
Who was the one pretending

150
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,790
to be mysterious first?

151
00:11:12,650 --> 00:11:15,080
I know you switched my people

152
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:17,000
and staged a show

153
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:18,360
at the succession ceremony.

154
00:11:21,670 --> 00:11:23,030
I've already looked around.

155
00:11:23,550 --> 00:11:25,080
There are traces
of explosives all around.

156
00:11:26,030 --> 00:11:28,240
Obviously, someone wants to kill you.

157
00:11:29,150 --> 00:11:30,510
Don't you mean both of us?

158
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,120
I'm not morally corrupt

159
00:11:32,910 --> 00:11:35,510
and have many enemies like you.

160
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,870
We are not the same.

161
00:11:40,670 --> 00:11:42,750
But you insist on groveling,

162
00:11:43,550 --> 00:11:46,910
stooping low to someone like me.

163
00:11:47,390 --> 00:11:48,750
Don't disturb me
while I'm investigating.

164
00:11:51,670 --> 00:11:52,200
Don't move.

165
00:12:19,630 --> 00:12:20,120
Who's there?

166
00:12:33,750 --> 00:12:34,480
Where did he go?

167
00:13:22,270 --> 00:13:22,790
Are you all right?

168
00:13:23,390 --> 00:13:24,200
I'm all right.

169
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:26,200
Watch out!

170
00:13:53,860 --> 00:13:57,620
♪The mountains and rivers I've seen
are painted on the fan♪

171
00:13:57,860 --> 00:14:01,020
♪The flowing clouds embrace
the wind and moon♪

172
00:14:01,300 --> 00:14:04,740
♪Longing immersed into the inkstone♪

173
00:14:04,980 --> 00:14:08,500
♪I foolishly think♪

174
00:14:08,580 --> 00:14:12,100
♪Unable to sleep, I was intoxicated
by the fragrance of books♪

175
00:14:12,220 --> 00:14:15,700
♪With you, the fragrance
fills the sky together♪

176
00:14:15,820 --> 00:14:21,580
♪Parting makes it hard
to express in many words♪

177
00:14:23,020 --> 00:14:26,780
♪I use tears to grind the residual moon
into the inkstone♪

178
00:14:26,860 --> 00:14:30,420
♪To write my longing
into every word and line♪

179
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:33,500
♪The past of my soul is full of dreams♪

180
00:14:33,580 --> 00:14:37,460
♪Like a broken mirror, hard to mend♪

181
00:14:37,820 --> 00:14:41,300
♪Half of my life is spent lingering
on paper and ink♪

182
00:14:41,380 --> 00:14:44,860
♪To describe the silent exchange
of glances between us♪

183
00:14:44,980 --> 00:14:51,620
♪Keeping hidden sorrows
and thoughts in the scrolls♪
